---
// HowItWorks.astro
---
<style>
  .hiw-section {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding: 80px 20px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
  }

  .hiw-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .hiw-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 60px auto;
  }

  .hiw-subtitle {
    color: #51acfb;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    display: block;
  }

  .hiw-title {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #252525;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .hiw-title span {
    color: #51acfb;
  }

  .hiw-desc {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hiw-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 40px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hiw-line {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: 60px;
    left: 15%;
    width: 70%;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(81,172,251,0.1) 0%, rgba(81,172,251,0.4) 50%, rgba(81,172,251,0.1) 100%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hiw-step {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .hiw-icon-box {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e5f1fc;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(81, 172, 251, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .hiw-step:hover .hiw-icon-box {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .hiw-icon-box svg {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    color: #51acfb;
  }

  .hiw-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -5px;
    right: -5px;
    width: 35px;
    height: 35px;
    background: #ef4c37;
    color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(239, 76, 55, 0.3);
    border: 4px solid #ffffff;
  }

  .hiw-step h3 {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #252525;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .hiw-step p {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  .hiw-cta {
    margin-top: 60px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .hiw-btn-call, .hiw-btn-whatsapp {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 16px 35px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .hiw-btn-call {
    background: #ef4c37;
    color: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(239, 76, 55, 0.2);
  }

  .hiw-btn-call:hover {
    background: #d8402c;
    color: #ffffff;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(239, 76, 55, 0.3);
  }

  .hiw-btn-call svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    margin-right: 10px;
  }

  .hiw-btn-whatsapp {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #252525;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .hiw-btn-whatsapp:hover {
    border-color: #252525;
    background: #fafafa;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .hiw-btn-whatsapp svg {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    margin-right: 10px;
    fill: #25D366;
  }

  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    .hiw-line {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .hiw-grid {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 50px;
    }
    
    .hiw-title {
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    
    .hiw-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    
    .hiw-btn-call, .hiw-btn-whatsapp {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="hiw-section">
  <div class="hiw-container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="hiw-header">
      <span class="hiw-subtitle">Processo Simples e Rápido</span>
      <h2 class="hiw-title">
        Como funciona o nosso <span>Serviço</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="hiw-desc">Em emergências, cada segundo conta. É por isso que simplificámos o nosso processo para que tenha ajuda profissional à sua porta no menor tempo possível sem confusões.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps -->
    <div class="hiw-grid">
      <!-- Connection line (desktop only) -->
      <div class="hiw-line"></div>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="hiw-step">
        <div class="hiw-icon-box">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
          </svg>
          <div class="hiw-badge">1</div>
        </div>
        <h3>Ligue ou Envie Mensagem</h3>
        <p>Contacte-nos por chamada gratuita ou WhatsApp. Estamos disponíveis 24/7 para ouvir o seu problema com atendimento humanizado e 100% imediato.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="hiw-step">
        <div class="hiw-icon-box">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7h12m0 0l3 5v6H3V7h5m12 0v6M3 13h18M5 16a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm14 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4z" />
          </svg>
          <div class="hiw-badge">2</div>
        </div>
        <h3>Deslocação Rápida</h3>
        <p>Com dezenas de veículos na estrada, ativamos o piquete profissional mais próximo de si para chegar à sua morada em tempo verdadeiramente recorde.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="hiw-step">
        <div class="hiw-icon-box">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
          </svg>
          <div class="hiw-badge">3</div>
        </div>
        <h3>Problema Resolvido</h3>
        <p>Atuamos de imediato no local. Sem tempos de espera, resolvemos a urgência no mesmo dia, garantindo um serviço impecavelmente limpo e com garantia.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="hiw-cta">
      <a href="tel:+351969146836" class="hiw-btn-call">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
        </svg> LIGUE JÁ: 969 146 836
      </a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/351969146836" target="_blank" class="hiw-btn-whatsapp">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51a12.8 12.8 0 00-.57-.01c-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413Z"/></svg> MENSAGEM WHATSAPP
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
